author: psmith
msg: Added a TestBed class that starts up log4j in a process, creates
a Zeroconf'd SocketHubAppender and starts streaming log messages to it.
Added beginnings of the ZeroConf plugin for Chainsaw. It detects when
ZeroConf enabled devices appear, and displays their details in a list model.
Eventually the user will be able to double click the discovered item to auto-create
